{
  "texts": [
    "However, the direct interpretation of the image data from figures remain difficult using the above method of data-mining from image.",
    "Machine learning has been used to predict the electrochemical mechanism involved in the reaction that expresses through a cyclic voltammogram (CV).",
    "Deep learning has also been used to distinguish the mechanism of the electrochemical reaction from CV based on residual neural network (ResNet) architecture and focused on analytical or fundamental electrochemistry.",
    "However, the application of machine learning to analyze electrochemical signals in the field of energy storage is still in its early stages.",
    "This study presents that electrochemical signal analysis (CV and GCD) has been performed using a machine learning (ML) approach based on image classification."
  ]
}